Install the xhost and xnest packages.

Ensure that /proc is mounted and DNS resolution is set-up within the chroot (see above).
Type the following into a Terminal: (terminal comum sem Chroot)

Xnest -ac :1

A blank Xnest window should appear.
Open another Terminal and type the following to enter the chroot:

	sudo chroot ~/Distro/custom (no de customização, o mesmo terminal em que está executando o chroot)

While in the chroot shell, type the following: (no terminal com Chroot)

export DISPLAY=localhost:1
		ou
export DISPLAY=127.0.0.1:1

   
